"title": "7925: fellowship, among believers",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7925: fellowship, among believers",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The fellowship that believers share as a result of their common union with God through Jesus Christ is expressed in life together. It is evident in worship together, in a love for one another which reflects God's own love and in a practical commitment to one another which is demonstrated in concern for the weak and readiness to share with the poor and needy.</p>\n<h2>Sharing in the fellowship of God's love</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:10-1John4:12\">1JN 4:10–4:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:34\">JHN 13:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:12\">JHN 15:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:1-Eph5:2\">EPH 5:1–5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:10\">1JN 3:10</a></p>\n<h2>Sharing in the fellowship of a common devotional life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:42\">ACT 2:42</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Worshipping together</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:14\">PSA 55:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:4\">PSA 42:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:26\">1CO 14:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:19\">EPH 5:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:16\">COL 3:16</a></p>\n<h3>Praying together</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:14\">ACT 1:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:24\">ACT 4:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:12\">ACT 12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:16\">JAS 5:16</a></p>\n<h3>Breaking bread together</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:16-1Cor10:17\">1CO 10:16–10:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:13\">2PE 2:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:12\">JUD 1:12</a> <em>Love feasts accompanied the Lord's Supper though these were open to abuse.</em></p>\n<h2>True fellowship means sharing with those in need</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:16\">HEB 13:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:34-Acts20:35\">ACT 20:34–20:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:28\">EPH 4:28</a></p>\n<h3>Showing hospitality</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:13\">ROM 12:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:7\">ISA 58:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:1-Heb13:2\">HEB 13:1–13:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:9\">1PE 4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:8\">3JN 1:8</a></p>\n<h3>Sharing money and possessions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut15:10-Deut15:11\">DEU 15:10–15:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:44-Acts2:45\">ACT 2:44–2:45</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:18-Deut10:19\">DEU 10:18–10:19</a> <em>God's people are to reflect his concern for the needy in society</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:35-Matt25:36\">MAT 25:35–25:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:11\">LUK 3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:32-Acts4:35\">ACT 4:32–4:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:13-2Cor8:15\">2CO 8:13–8:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17-1Tim6:18\">1TI 6:17–6:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:27\">JAS 1:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:15-Jas2:16\">JAS 2:15–2:16</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of sharing with the needy</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:16-Job31:20\">JOB 31:16–31:20</a> <em>Job's compassion for the needy</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:1\">ACT 6:1</a> <em>the daily distribution to widows</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:36\">ACT 9:36</a> <em>Tabitha's concern for the poor</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:29-Acts11:30\">ACT 11:29–11:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:26\">ROM 15:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:3-2Cor8:4\">2CO 8:3–8:4</a></p>\n<h2>Strengthening one another in fellowship together</h2>\n<h3>Bearing with the weak</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:1-Gal6:2\">GAL 6:1–6:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:3\">ISA 42:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:1\">ROM 14:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:1\">ROM 15:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:14\">1TH 5:14</a></p>\n<h3>Strengthening the weak</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:3-Isa35:4\">ISA 35:3–35:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:3-Job4:4\">JOB 4:3–4:4</a></p>\n<h3>Encouraging one another</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:24-Heb10:25\">HEB 10:24–10:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:16\">1SA 23:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:12\">ROM 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:11\">1TH 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:3\">HEB 13:3</a></p>\n<h3>Putting the needs of others first</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:2\">ROM 15:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:24\">1CO 10:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:32-1Cor10:33\">1CO 10:32–10:33</a></p>\n<h2>True fellowship means living in harmony</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:8\">1PE 3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:16\">ROM 12:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:2-Eph4:3\">EPH 4:2–4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:1-Phil2:4\">PHP 2:1–2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:12-Col3:14\">COL 3:12–3:14</a></p>\n<h3>Showing equal concern for all</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:34\">ACT 10:34</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:25\">1CO 12:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:1-Jas2:4\">JAS 2:1–2:4</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of fellowship</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num10:31-Num10:32\">NUM 10:31–10:32</a> <em>Moses and Hobab</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:3\">1SA 18:3</a> <em>David and Jonathan</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:15-2Kgs10:16\">2KI 10:15–10:16</a> <em>Jehu and Jehonadab</em></p>\n<h3>Failure to exhibit true fellowship</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam30:22\">1SA 30:22</a> <em>Troublemakers in David's army are unwilling to share the spoils</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:11-1Cor1:12\">1CO 1:11–1:12</a> <em>factions within the church at Corinth</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:17-1Cor11:22\">1CO 11:17–11:22</a> <em>Selfishness at love feasts humiliates the poor.</em></p>",
